@node "History" "Historique"

        @{b}Program history@{ub}
        ===============


Summer 1993    V0.0        : Start of the development of 'Lynx'.

October, 1993  V0.5        : Most of the image processes implanted
                             First version of the graphical interface.

November, 1993 V0.6        : Fast Fourier Transform implanted !!
                             First On-Line help. Not very great. Quickly
                             canceled.

Januar, 1994   V0.7        : Visualisation of color images.
                             Reading of IFF files.

Februar, 1994  V0.8        : Firsts Multichanels processes.
                             Reading and writing of some stranges
                             image formats.

May, 1994      V0.9        : ARexx port implanted.
                             3.0+ compatible? Use of 3.0 functions for
                             visualisation.

April, 1995    V1.00a_I    : First alpha-version.

20/05/95                   : V1.0Ŗ first beta-release. French documen-
                             tation only. Except this page !

--
@endnode

